platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: There’s a lot to love in Sago Mini School, but here’s the secret ingredient: It’s designed in collaboration with leading child development experts. The app offers kids the opportunity to problem-solve and think creatively as they explore topics such as reading, writing, and math—all with the help of Sago Mini’s signature characters.
